Sylly
=====

Daily lecture:  15-20 min live coding, and then 5-10 minute START to a practice chunk of code.
These practice chunks won't graded.  But encouraged to complete them.

What will graded are 3 different installment to one large software project.

Weighted:  20% 20% 20% = 60% of the course grade

And then a final EXAM will be the remaining 40%.

Must pass the exam (60%).

Typical late penalties:  10% first day, 15% second day, 40% third day.  Negotiable if in good standing.

Textbook:  is the man pages.
